I am working on a generic swerve implementation that will hopefully be very easy for everyone once we get the documentation made. My teams batteries were all dead (12.3v and bellow) when we were testing the drive today, I have amperage limits on it and enabled voltage compensation etc. I would like to know what i should be aware of for a SDS Mk4 all Neo’s base.
